claim.claim-text:
3. A barcode creation apparatus, comprising:
a color specification device which specifies a color of a two-dimensional barcode according to color information of an object into which the barcode is to be embedded;
an arrangement determination device which determines a position in which to embed the barcode according to the specified color of the barcode and the color information of the object into which the barcode is to be embedded; and
a barcode creation device which creates the barcode with the color specified by the color specification device;
wherein the object to include the barcode is an image, and the image is scanned by blocks corresponding to a shape of the two-dimensional barcode, and wherein a block having a color tone deviation range which is equal to or less than a prescribed value is determined from the scanned blocks as corresponding to the position in which the barcode is to be embedded.

7. A barcode creation method, comprising the steps of:
specifying a color of a two-dimensional barcode according to color information of an object into which the barcode is to be embedded;
determining a position in which to embed the barcode according to the specified color of the barcode and the color information of the object into which the barcode is to be embedded; and
creating the barcode in the specified color;
wherein the object to include the barcode is an image, and the image is scanned by blocks corresponding to a shape of the two-dimensional barcode, and wherein a block having a color tone deviation range which is equal to or less than a prescribed value is determined from the scanned blocks as corresponding to the position in which the barcode is to be embedded.

11. A computer readable medium having embodied thereon a computer program for processing by a computer, the computer program comprising:
a first code segment for specifying a color of a two-dimensional barcode according to color information of an object into which the barcode is to be embedded;
a second code segment for determining a position in which to embed the barcode according to the specified color of the barcode and the color information of the object into which the barcode is to be embedded; and
a third code segment for creating the barcode in the specified color;
wherein the object to include the barcode is an image, and the image is scanned by blocks corresponding to a shape of the two-dimensional barcode, and wherein a block having a color tone deviation range which is equal to or less than a prescribed value is determined from the scanned blocks as corresponding to the position in which the barcode is to be embedded.
